# Session [3] – Network+

## Main Topics
- Bridge chist? (What is Bridge?)
- Bridge chetor kar mikonad? (How does Bridge work?)
- Fargh bridge ba hub va switch chist? ( what is the difrence between hub and switch?)

## Flashback – Bridge Basics
- Bridge = device ke 2 ya bishtar network segment ra be ham vasl mikonad
- Bridge traffic ra filter mikonad va faghat data mored nazar ra be segment dige mifrestad
- Estefade baraye **reduce traffic** va **improve performance**

## Explanation
- Bridge = hardware baraye network
- Ham PC ha ra be ham vasl mikonad vali smart tar az hub
- Data ra **faghat be segment mored nazar** miresand, na be tamame network
- Fargh ba switch:
  - Switch be har port PC ya device ra address mikonad, bridge be segment ha
- Estefade dar LAN haye bozorg ke mikhahand traffic ro control k

